::: TRANSACTIONS SIMULATION WITH BITCOINS :::

compile: make

clean: make clean

compile manually: gcc -o bitcoin main.c bitcoin.c hash.c list.c transaction.c wallet.c

run examples:

./bitcoin -a resources/bitCoinBalancesFile -v 50 -h1 10 -h2 10 -b 51 -t resources/transactionsFile

./bitcoin -a resources/SimplebitCoinBalanciesFIle -v 50 -h1 10 -h2 10 -b 51 -t resources/transactionsFile

documentation: open 'documentation.pdf' file.